snippet.title: Music Catch 2 - Through the Fire and Flames
snippet.description:
Play the game here: http://www.kongregate.com/games/Reflexive/music-catch-2?referrer=Xarthok

Obviously YouTube disabled the audio so I chose a nice classical tune to go with this ;)

Anyway, this is the sequel to the relaxing game Music Catch. You can use your own MP3s to play with once you unlock that option by playing through all the modes. So, lots of fun!

I got 26.1 million score, 88% hits and 259x multiplier.
